data.description: Welcome to this charming raised ranch home on a 1/2-acre lot. This cozy floor plan creates a spacious and inviting atmosphere.The great room features a stone fireplace.The Dining area and kitchen seamlessly blend together for holiday entertaining with an additional large deck perfect for grilling and relaxing. A spacious mudroom is right off the kitchen which has laundry access. An unfinished basement is ready for your future expansion. Newer architectural shingle roof is less than 2 years old. The exterior of the home boasts vinyl siding and a 2 car side entry garage. Enjoy the outdoors in your level back yard. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home before the year ends!
